.0178%3Atext%3DGorg.%3Asection%3D447a (translation)] from {{cite book\n  | last = Plato\n  | others = John Burnet (ed.)\n  | title = Platonis Opera\n  | publisher = Oxford University Press\n  | year = 1903\n  }}\n* Plato, ''Menexenus''. See original text in [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0179%3Atext%3DMenex.%3Asection%3D236a Perseus program] [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0180%3Atext%3DMenex.%3Asection%3D236a (translation)] from {{cite book\n  | last = Plato\n  | others = W.R.M. Lamb (trans.)\n  | title = Plato in Twelve Volumes, Vol. 9\n  | publisher = Harvard University Press\n  | year = 1925\n  | location = Cambridge, MA\n  | isbn = 978-0-674-99185-9}}\n* Plato, ''[[Phaedrus (dialogue)|Phaedrus]]'', See original text in [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0173%3Atext%3DPhaedrus%3Asection%3D270a Perseus program] [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0174%3Atext%3DPhaedrus%3Asection%3D270a (translation)] from {{cite book\n  | last = Plato\n  | others = John Burnet (ed.)\n  | title = Platonis Opera\n  | publisher = Oxford University Press\n  | year = 1903\n  }}\n* Plutarch, ''Cimon''. See original text in [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A2008.01.0069%3Achapter%3D17%3Asection%3D6 Perseus program] [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A2008.01.0017%3Achapter%3D17%3Asection%3D6 (translation)]\n* {{cite wikisource |author=[[Plutarch]] |wslink=Lives (Dryden translation) |plaintitle=Lives |chapter=Pericles |translator=[[John Dryden]]}}. See original text in [http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3atext%3a2008.01.0072 Perseus program]\n* Quintilian, ''Institutiones''. See original text in [http://www.thelatinlibrary.com/quintilian.html The Latin Library].\n* {{cite wikisource |title=History of the Peloponnesian War |author=[[Thucydides]] |translator=[[Richard 